      "content": "it just feels like there's no way to make it better for them. i've lived a long life and i've seen them grow up, but now i'm just the thing they have to manage. sometimes i wonder if they'd actually be more at peace if they didn't have to worry about me anymore. if i wasn't here, they could just focus on their own lives without this constant worry. does that sound selfish?",
